## Product Tiers

**Meridian Core** — Real-time PSI monitor. 7 behavioral signal dimensions. Personal adaptive baseline. 5-year local session history. Post-session report. No cloud.

**Meridian Guard** — Everything in Core, plus: Guard System (6 trigger types, 5 intervention levels including automated broker disconnect), Intel Layer (monthly digest, PSI × P&L correlation, weekday patterns, Today's Risk Brief).

